  "response": "Yes, in an Instagram group chat, all members of the group can see any messages that you send. Group messages are visible to everyone in the group, so if you send a message, all other members will receive it and be able to read it. If you're looking to have a private conversation with someone, it's best to send a direct message to that individual rather than posting in a group chat.",
